This directory contains the source for the "bundy-init" program, as well as
the "bundy" script that runs it.

Files:
  Makefile.am      - build information
  README           - this file
  TODO             - remaining development tasks for this program
  bundy.py.in     - used to make bundy.py with proper Python paths
  init.spec        - defines the options and commands
  run_bundy.sh.in - use to make run_bundy.sh with proper Python paths

The "tests" directory contains unit tests for the application.

If you want to run the bundy program from the source directory, then
use the "run_bundy.sh" script. To run it in the installed location,
use the "bundy" program.
